WEBVTT

00:04.001 --> 00:10.500
From space, it seems an abstraction, a
magician's trick on a darkened stage.

00:10.500 --> 00:15.500
And from this distance one might
never imagine that it is alive.

00:17.000 --> 00:24.800
It first appeared in the sea almost four billion
years ago in the form of single-celled life.

00:24.800 --> 00:27.400
In an explosion of life spanning
millions of years, ...

00:27.400 --> 00:35.000
...nature's first multicellular organisms
began to multiply... and then it stopped.

00:35.000 --> 00:40.800
440 million years ago, a great mass extinction
would kill off nearly every species...

00:40.800 --> 00:46.700
...on the planet leaving the vast
oceans decimated and empty.

00:46.700 --> 00:51.800
Slowly, plants began to evolve,
then insects, ...

00:51.800 --> 00:57.500
...only to be wiped out in the second
great mass extinction upon the Earth.

00:57.500 --> 01:00.500
The cycle repeated again and again.

01:00.500 --> 01:05.800
Reptiles emerging, independent of
the sea only to be killed off.

01:05.800 --> 01:13.000
Then dinosaurs, struggling to life along with
the first birds, fish, and flowering plants...

01:13.000 --> 01:19.400
...their decimations Earth's fourth
and fifth great extinctions.

01:19.700 --> 01:25.800
Only 100,000 years ago,
Homo Sapiens appear... man.

01:25.800 --> 01:30.400
From cave paintings to the Bible
to Columbus and Apollo 11, ...

01:30.400 --> 01:34.800
...we have been a tireless force
upon the earth and off...

01:34.800 --> 01:39.400
...cataloguing the natural world
as it unfolds to us.

01:39.400 --> 01:43.200
Rising to a world population
of over five billion people...

01:43.200 --> 01:49.300
...all descended from that original single
cell, that first spark of life.

01:50.800 --> 01:54.800
But for all our knowledge, what no
one can say for certain, ...

01:54.800 --> 01:59.900
...is what or who ignited
that original spark.

01:59.900 --> 02:05.800
Is there a plan, a purpose or a
reason to our existence?

02:05.800 --> 02:10.800
Will we pass, as those before us,
into oblivion, ...

02:10.800 --> 02:15.700
...into the sixth extinction that
scientists warn is already in progress?

